    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>YR8.6 Var. a (mss. 300, 360, 370, Ms. 300):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> sē guftan srōšdrōn xwardan ud dahān pāk kardan ud dast pad pādyāb kardan <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> čahār guftan</ab> 
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "He should say three <em>Aṣ̌əm Vohū</em>, eat the <em>srōšdrōn</em>, clean his mouth and wash his (right) hand with <em>pādyāb</em>. 
                Then he should recite the <em>Aṣ̌əm Vohū</em> four times."</ab>
            <ab>YR8.6 Var. b (ms. 365):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> sə -:- cāšniikaradan. paṣ̌. <em>aṣ̌əm vōhū</em> cāhr</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "He (says) three <em>Aṣ̌əm Vohū</em>. He should make <em>čāšnī</em> and then he (says) four <em>Aṣ̌əm Vohū</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
    </Ritual>
